{"type": "article", "id": 30168, "title": "像是棕榈叶的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-26T23:02:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160726203537JSlrpBzoHF9ymNUd.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p><a href=\"http://www.studioforma.ch/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studioforma</a> 最近为意大利品牌 <a href=\"http://www.meroniecolzani.it/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meroni &amp; Colzani</a> 设计了一款具有热带风情的椅子 <a href=\"http://www.sfdesignlab.com/pile_portfolio/pam/\" rel=\"nofollow\">PAM</a>，流畅的线条以及管状结构使它看上去就好像是一张巨大的棕榈叶。椅子由工匠在以家具生产而闻名的布里安扎地区（Brianza）采用核桃木手工制作而成，椅腿和座位之间无缝相连，整体造型简洁优雅。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607262046285JMiBdRKPzgFyUtv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.610000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726204628nFGyd7vzfx65Duho.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726204628zU5dK6jEFMaSbZ17.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726204629Q1L6wNlXnE7p53fC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}